After one of these successes, I happened upon Krystall in Nektulos again when a Druid Wood Elf had the gaul to enter our forest and tempt Innoruuk. The Stone Guards came to kill him but I saw an opportunity to capture his soul into my father’s service by healing him during the battle. All did not go as planned though for as I was healing him, guards came at me from behind and tried to strike me down. Krystall struck the guard and called for me to flee for my life. I gated to the gates of that foul Human city called Freeport then healed myself.<br>
<br>
This is how I came to serve Krystall and the House of Ecllypse for I owe her my very life. Her constant companion and healer.<br>
<br>
The killing continues in my father’s name, Innoruuk.<br>
